---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="Interactive APS Tools" 
  description="Interactive web tools for Autodesk Platform Services development, including OAuth scope builders, token decoders, cost estimators, and debugging tools."
>
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-display font-bold text-white mb-4">
        Interactive APS Tools
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-3xl">
        Browser-based tools to simplify APS development. Build scopes, decode tokens, 
        estimate costs, debug translations, and encode URNs - all with RAPS CLI alternatives.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-8 bg-blue-950/30 border border-blue-800/30 rounded-xl p-6">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="text-blue-400 mt-1">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-blue-300 mb-2">üí° RAPS CLI Alternative</h3>
          <p class="text-blue-200 mb-2">
            All these web tools have command-line equivalents in RAPS CLI for automation and scripting:
          </p>
          <div class="bg-slate-900/50 rounded-lg p-3 font-mono text-sm">
            <div class="text-slate-400">raps auth login --scopes data:read,viewables:read</div>
            <div class="text-slate-400">raps urn encode "urn:adsk.objects:os.object:bucket/file.dwg"</div>
            <div class="text-slate-400">raps translate status &lt;urn&gt; --diagnose</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
      <!-- OAuth Scope Builder -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-rapeseed-400/30 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="mb-4">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">üîê</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-rapeseed-400 transition-colors">
            OAuth Scope Builder
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Interactive tool to build and validate APS OAuth scope combinations for 2-legged and 3-legged authentication flows.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="bg-rapeseed-400/10 text-rapeseed-400 px-2 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium">OAuth</span>
          <span class="bg-blue-400/10 text-blue-400 px-2 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium">Scopes</span>
          <span class="bg-green-400/10 text-green-400 px-2 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium">Authentication</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <a 
            href="/tools/scope-builder" 
            class="bg-rapeseed-500 hover:bg-rapeseed-600 text-slate-900 font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors"
          >
            Build Scopes
          </a>
          <div class="text-slate-400 text-xs">
            CLI: <code class="bg-slate-800 px-1 rounded text-rapeseed-400">raps auth</code>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- JWT Token Decoder -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-rapeseed-400/30 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="mb-4">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">üîì</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-rapeseed-400 transition-colors">
            JWT Token Decoder
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Decode and analyze APS JWT authentication tokens to understand scopes, expiration, and token structure.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="bg-rapeseed-400/10 text-rapeseed-400 px-2 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium">JWT</span>
          <span class="bg-purple-400/10 text-purple-400 px-2 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium">Token</span>
          <span class="bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-400 px-2 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium">Debug</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <a 
            href="/tools/token-decoder" 
            class="bg-rapeseed-500 hover:bg-rapeseed-600 text-slate-900 font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors"
          >
            Decode Token
          </a>
          <div class="text-slate-400 text-xs">
            CLI: <code class="bg-slate-800 px-1 rounded text-rapeseed-400">raps auth status</code>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Token Cost Estimator -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-rapeseed-400/30 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="mb-4">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">üí∞</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-rapeseed-400 transition-colors">
            Token Cost Estimator
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Calculate monthly APS token costs for Model Derivative translations and Design Automation operations.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="bg-green-400/10 text-green-400 px-2 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium">Cost</span>
          <span class="bg-yellow-400/10 text-yellow-400 px-2 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium">Pricing</span>
          <span class="bg-blue-400/10 text-blue-400 px-2 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium">Planning</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <a 
            href="/tools/token-estimator" 
            class="bg-rapeseed-500 hover:bg-rapeseed-600 text-slate-900 font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors"
          >
            Estimate Costs
          </a>
          <div class="text-slate-400 text-xs">
            CLI: <code class="bg-slate-800 px-1 rounded text-rapeseed-400">raps cost</code>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Translation Debugger -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-rapeseed-400/30 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="mb-4">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">üîç</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-rapeseed-400 transition-colors">
            Translation Debugger
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Debug APS Model Derivative translation failures with human-readable explanations and solutions.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="bg-red-400/10 text-red-400 px-2 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium">Debug</span>
          <span class="bg-purple-400/10 text-purple-400 px-2 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium">Translation</span>
          <span class="bg-orange-400/10 text-orange-400 px-2 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium">Diagnosis</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <a 
            href="/tools/translation-debugger" 
            class="bg-rapeseed-500 hover:bg-rapeseed-600 text-slate-900 font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors"
          >
            Debug Translation
          </a>
          <div class="text-slate-400 text-xs">
            CLI: <code class="bg-slate-800 px-1 rounded text-rapeseed-400">raps translate</code>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- URN Encoder/Decoder -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 hover:border-rapeseed-400/30 transition-all duration-300 group">
        <div class="mb-4">
          <div class="text-3xl mb-3">üõ†Ô∏è</div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2 group-hover:text-rapeseed-400 transition-colors">
            URN Encoder/Decoder
          </h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            Encode and decode APS URNs with base64 URL-safe encoding for API calls and file identification.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
          <span class="bg-blue-400/10 text-blue-400 px-2 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium">URN</span>
          <span class="bg-green-400/10 text-green-400 px-2 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium">Base64</span>
          <span class="bg-yellow-400/10 text-yellow-400 px-2 py-1 rounded-md text-xs font-medium">Encoding</span>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
          <a 
            href="/tools/urn-encoder" 
            class="bg-rapeseed-500 hover:bg-rapeseed-600 text-slate-900 font-medium px-4 py-2 rounded-lg transition-colors"
          >
            Encode/Decode URN
          </a>
          <div class="text-slate-400 text-xs">
            CLI: <code class="bg-slate-800 px-1 rounded text-rapeseed-400">raps urn</code>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Future Tools Placeholder -->
      <div class="bg-slate-900/30 border border-slate-800/50 border-dashed rounded-xl p-6 flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="text-slate-600 text-4xl mb-3">‚öôÔ∏è</div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-500 mb-2">More Tools Coming Soon</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">
            Additional developer tools are in development
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Features Section -->
    <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-slate-900/30 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span>üöÄ</span>
          Why Use These Tools?
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-slate-300">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-rapeseed-400 mt-1">‚Ä¢</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">No Installation Required:</strong> Run directly in your browser</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-rapeseed-400 mt-1">‚Ä¢</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Privacy First:</strong> All processing happens locally, no data sent to servers</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-rapeseed-400 mt-1">‚Ä¢</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">CLI Integration:</strong> Every tool has a RAPS CLI equivalent for automation</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-rapeseed-400 mt-1">‚Ä¢</span>
            <span><strong class="text-white">Developer Focused:</strong> Built by APS developers, for APS developers</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-slate-900/30 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span>‚ö°</span>
          Getting Started
        </h3>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-slate-300">
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-white font-medium mb-1">1. Start with OAuth Scopes</h4>
            <p class="text-sm">Build the correct scope combination for your APS application</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-white font-medium mb-1">2. Understand Your Tokens</h4>
            <p class="text-sm">Decode JWT tokens to verify scopes and expiration times</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-white font-medium mb-1">3. Estimate Costs</h4>
            <p class="text-sm">Plan your budget with accurate token cost calculations</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-white font-medium mb-1">4. Debug Issues</h4>
            <p class="text-sm">Use the debugger when translations fail or URNs need encoding</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>